the rating outlook is stable. both tpc and tighis long-term issuer ratings and senior debt have been removed from rating watch negative and downgraded to a- from a. for all debt ratings, the rating outlook is stable. fitch also removed the st.
paul travelers companies, inc. from rating watch positive and upgraded the senior debt rating to a- from bbb with a stable outlook.   on june 29, 2004, a.m. best announced the following ratings changes:
