buildings, land, and other commercial real estate assets that are directly owned. the company negotiates commercial leases with individual tenants through unrelated, licensed real estate brokers. negotiated terms and conditions include, among
others, rental rates, length of lease period and improvements to the premises to be provided by the landlord.   future minimum rental income expected on operating leases relating to the companys real estate properties is $95 million, $82 million, $69 million,
