23.
subsequent event   on january 31, 2005, the company announced its intention to explore alternatives for divestiture of ownership of its 79% share of nuveen investments, an
asset management franchise. the proposed divestiture reflects the companys strategic decision to focus on its property-casualty business. the company anticipates a disposition within twelve months.
