ther information   on january 25, 2005, the compensation committee (compensation committee) of the board of directors of the company approved the annual base salaries, annual incentive (i.e., cash bonus) awards, awards of restricted stock made pursuant to the
companys capital accumulation program (cap), stock option grants and other restricted stock grants for executive officers of the company.   salary and cash bonus   the following table sets forth the annual base salaries as of the end of 2004 and for 2005 for the companys chief executive officer and the four
