(3)
these are shares available for grant as of december 31, 2004 under the 2004 plan pursuant to which the compensation committee of the board of directors may make various stock-based
awards including grants of stock options, restricted stock and stock appreciation rights. the 2004 plan had 35 million shares initially authorized for issuance. in addition to these 35 million shares, the following shares will become available for
